# launch-smoke.ad — minimal launch smoke check.
#
# NOTE: This is a hand-authored placeholder so CI has something to run. `.ad`
# checks are normally produced by the recorder — replace this with a proper
# recording via `yarn e2e:record` once you have a booted device with the app.
#
# It opens the app on a booted simulator/emulator and asserts that the Login
# screen renders on first launch (see src/Scenes/Login/Login.tsx).

open Energy
wait "Log In"
is "Folio"
close
